            f(x) &amp;=&amp; \\left( x^2 + \\dfrac{x}{ \\sqrt{1 + x^2} } \\right) \\left( 1 + \\dfrac{x}{ (1 + x^2) \\sqrt{1 + x^2} } \\right) \\\\
                        &amp;=&amp; x^2 + \\frac{x}{\\sqrt{1+x^2}} + \\frac{x^3}{\\left( 1 + x^2 \\right)\\sqrt{1+x^2}} + \\frac{x^2}{\\left(1 + x^2 \\right)^2} \\\\
